                                            Alex woke on her own around 730am and took herself to the bathroom.
                                        </li>
                                        <li draggable
                                            onDragStart={(e) => handleDragStart(e, 'Alex woke at 600am, went to bathroom, and went back to bed. ')}>Alex
                                            woke at 600am, went to bathroom, and went back to bed.
